, 0) !important;\'>//cache路径</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\'color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"SF Pro Display\", Roboto, Noto, Arial, \"PingFang SC\", sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'><span style=\'color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"SF Pro Display\", Roboto, Noto, Arial, \"PingFang SC\", sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\'><span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"SF Pro Display\", Roboto, Noto, Arial, \"PingFang SC\", sans-serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; white-space: pre; color: rgb(136, 0, 0) !important;\'><br></span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p>进入环境变量对话框，在系统变量下新建&rdquo;NODE_PATH&rdquo;，输入&rdquo;XXXX\\npm_modules\\node_modules&ldquo;。&nbsp;</p><p>由于改变了module的默认地址，所以上面的用户变量都要跟着改变一下&nbsp;</p><p>（用户变量&rdquo;PATH&rdquo;修改为&ldquo;XXXX\\npm_modules&rdquo;）</p><p><br></p><p>安装淘宝镜像</p><p><span style=\'color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: \"Source Code Pro\", \"DejaVu Sans Mono\", \"Ubuntu Mono\", \"Anonymous Pro\", \"Droid Sans Mono\", Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace, \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; white-space: pre; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250);\'>npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry</span><span class=\"hljs-preprocessor\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"SF Pro Display\", Roboto, Noto, Arial, \"PingFang SC\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; white-space: pre; color: rgb(0, 153, 0) !important;\'>.npm</span><span class=\"hljs-preprocessor\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"SF Pro Display\", Roboto, Noto, Arial, \"PingFang SC\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; white-space: pre; color: rgb(0, 153, 0) !important;\'>.taobao</span><span class=\"hljs-preprocessor\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"SF Pro Display\", Roboto, Noto, Arial, \"PingFang SC\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; white-space: pre; color: rgb(0, 153, 0) !important;\'>.org</span></p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '2019-06-26 14:20:41', 'tom', '1');
INSERT INTO `stu_demo_code` VALUES ('4028d8816bd9a625016bd9a9a2ba0000', 'npm,dva,下载包报错,', '错误记录', '1', '<p>当发现项目中用到了包 没有报错 需要 npm install XXXX --save&nbsp; 如果报错就删除目录下的文件夹重新下载</p><p>或者说 package.json里面报错包不在就可以这样安装</p><p><br/></p>', '2019-07-10 10:15:01', 'tom', '0');
INSERT INTO `stu_demo_code` VALUES ('4ad3889780374e1ca03b0653ed31dbbc', 'js追加样式；js里的()和[]；', '知识记录', '0', '<pre style=\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 20px; border: 1px dotted rgb(119, 136, 85); font-family: Consolas; width: 765px; background: rgb(245, 245, 245); line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">$(&quot;p&quot;).css(&quot;background-color&quot;,&quot;yellow&quot;);</pre><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 8px 18px; border: none; line-height: 21px; display: inline-block; outline: 0px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(233, 104, 107); text-align: center; transition: all 0.2s ease-out 0s; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 6px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24) 0px 1px 2px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">设置css</p><pre style=\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 20px; border: 1px dotted rgb(119, 136, 85); font-family: Consolas; width: 765px; background: rgb(245, 245, 245); line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">$(&quot;p&quot;).css(&quot;background-color&quot;);</pre><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 8px 18px; border: none; line-height: 21px; display: inline-block; outline: 0px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(233, 104, 107); text-align: center; transition: all 0.2s ease-out 0s; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 6px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24) 0px 1px 2px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">获取css</p><pre style=\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 20px; border: 1px dotted rgb(119, 136, 85); font-family: Consolas; width: 765px; background: rgb(245, 245, 245); line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">$(&quot;p&quot;).css({&quot;background-color&quot;:&quot;yellow&quot;,&quot;font-size&quot;:&quot;200%&quot;});</pre><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 8px 18px; border: none; line-height: 21px; display: inline-block; outline: 0px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(233, 104, 107); text-align: left; transition: all 0.2s ease-out 0s; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 6px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24) 0px 1px 2px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">设置多个css</p><hr><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\">js中[]、{}、()区别</span></strong></p><p><strong style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"SF Pro Display\", Roboto, Noto, Arial, \"PingFang SC\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(245, 246, 247); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>{ } 大括号，表示定义一个对象，大部分情况下要有成对的属性和值，或是函数体</strong>&nbsp;</p><p><strong style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", \"SF Pro Display\", Roboto, Noto, Arial, \"PingFang SC\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(245, 246, 247); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>[ ]中括号，表示一个数组，也可以理解为一个数组对象</strong>&nbsp;</p><hr><p><br></p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '2019-12-18 16:41:19', 'tom', '2');
INSERT INTO `stu_demo_code` VALUES ('765bbfa2284f49a8882dfc1998a2706e', 'promise', '知识记录', '0', '<h2>例子：</h2><p><img src=\"http://192.168.0.226:8821//EasyTom/data/2019/12/23/c6b471a391ad42448d63b4b0bffa4047.png\" style=\"width: 437px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-fil fr-dii\" data-id=\"765bbfa2284f49a8882dfc1998a2706e\"></p><p><img src=\"http://192.168.0.226:8821//EasyTom/data/2019/12/23/57db40e41d394203b30058dc36071bb1.png\" style=\"width: 400px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-fil fr-dii\" data-id=\"765bbfa2284f49a8882dfc1998a2706e\"><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>结果分别为 sucess 666&nbsp; &nbsp;；&nbsp; &nbsp;error&nbsp; 888</p><hr><p>如果promise里有其他代码，那么先执行其他代码最后执行reject。。。 除非直接return reject()；</p><hr><pre style=\'overflow: auto; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, \"Andale Mono\", monospace; font-size: 15.36px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 0px 1px; direction: ltr; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: 0px; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; padding: 10px 1em 10px 0.7rem; margin: 0.5em auto; border-radius: 5px; background: rgb(17, 17, 17); line-height: 1.2; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><code style=\'font-family: Consolas, \"Courier New\", Courier, FreeMono, monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgb(166, 226, 46); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 0px 1px; direction: ltr; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; font-weight: normal; background: rgb(17, 17, 17); border-radius: 2px;\'>promise\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">.</span>then<span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">(</span>result <span style=\"color: rgb(249, 38, 114);\">=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 38, 114);\">&gt;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">{</span>&middot;&middot;&middot;<span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">}</span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">)</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 217, 239);\">catch</span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">(</span>error <span style=\"color: rgb(249, 38, 114);\">=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 38, 114);\">&gt;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">{</span>&middot;&middot;&middot;<span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">}</span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">)</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 217, 239);\">finally</span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">(</span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">(</span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">)</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(249, 38, 114);\">=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 38, 114);\">&gt;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">{</span>&middot;&middot;&middot;<span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">}</span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">)</span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 242);\">;</span></code></pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 15.36px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">上面代码中，不管</span><code style=\'font-family: Consolas, \"Courier New\", Courier, FreeMono, monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); font-weight: 400; background: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding-left: 3px; padding-right: 3px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>promise</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 15.36px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">最后的状态，在执行完</span><code style=\'font-family: Consolas, \"Courier New\", Courier, FreeMono, monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); font-weight: 400; background: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding-left: 3px; padding-right: 3px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>then</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 15.36px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">或</span><code style=\'font-family: Consolas, \"Courier New\", Courier, FreeMono, monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); font-weight: 400; background: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding-left: 3px; padding-right: 3px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>catch</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 15.36px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">指定的回调函数以后，都会执行</span><code style=\'font-family: Consolas, \"Courier New\", Courier, FreeMono, monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); font-weight: 400; background: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding-left: 3px; padding-right: 3px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>finally</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 15.36px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">方法指定的回调函数。</span>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 15.36px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">ES2018 引入标准的</span>&nbsp;</p><hr><p><strong>应用：</strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"http://192.168.0.226:8821//EasyTom/data/2019/12/24/1ec64d36a2894020b4a39eab1a81bfee.png\" style=\"width: 629px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib fr-fil\" data-id=\"765bbfa2284f49a8882dfc1998a2706e\"></strong><br></p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '2019-12-23 16:51:13', 'tom', '2');
